HEADWORD: Hibernal
<hw>Hi*ber"nal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>hibernalis</ets>, from the root of <ets>hiems</ets> winter; akin to
Gr. <?/ snow, Skr. <ets>hima</ets> cold, winter, snow: cf. F.
<ets>hibernal</ets>.]</ety> <def>Belonging or relating to winter;
